input: Algorithmic game theory by professor Bryce

a spectrum of Cognitive Support:
| Level | Strategy | Goal |
|---|---|---|
| Directive | "Give me the answer." | Efficiency and immediate information retrieval. |
| Scaffolded | "Give me the answer and explain the steps." | Understanding the "how" behind the result. |
| Socratic | "Don't give the answer; ask me questions to lead me there." | Building independent problem-solving skills and critical thinking. |
| Metacognitive | "Analyze my reasoning process for errors." | High-fidelity thinking and self-correction. |
